Package eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.block.aggregating

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Average
    Compute the average of the integer or real values within the collection.
    Count
    Counts the elements in the given collection.
    Max
    Returns the largest value in the collection along with its last occurrence.
    MaxAll
    Returns the largest value from the collection along with the collection of its occurrence indexes.
    Min
    Returns the smallest value in the collection along with its last occurrence.
    MinAll
    Returns the smallest value from the collection along with the collection of its occurrence indexes.
    STDDeviation
    Computes the standard deviation of numerical elements of the supplied collection.
    Sum
    Compute the sum of the elements within the collection which have the type of Integer or Real.
